00:39:34.872 --> 00:39:36.473
-Ha?  
-(şaşkınlık sesi)

00:39:39.877 --> 00:39:42.412
-(nefesi kesilir)  
-(kıkırdar)

00:39:42.447 --> 00:39:44.481
♪ ♪

00:39:54.892 --> 00:39:57.727
KADIN (anondu):  
Jingu Gaien havai fişekleri

00:39:57.762 --> 00:40:01.431
